(339, 'arrive', 'normal', 'non', '2018-09-25', '2018-11-19', 'WILLIAMS COLLEGE', 'S/R', NULL, 5, 'Système d\'information', 'Asking for a meeting', 1, '0240', 'Williams College is an institution in Massachusetts, known and specialized in master’s degree program in economics for public sector. The college is now accepting applications for the August 2019 to June 2020 session, and scholarship funding is available. The Director Thomas Powers (remembered Mr Curtis in Washinton) is planning to visit Conakry from 21 to 25 Nov to provide further information. He would like to schedule a time to meet with the Minister in charge of IPPP on 22 or 23 Nov 2018. Mr Camara can be reached regarding the meeting.', '2018-10-23', '2018-11-19 17:05:50', '0240', '0', NULL, 3, 'upload/1538747285.pdf', '2018-10-05 11:48:06', '2018-11-19 17:05:50', NULL),
